{
  "info": {
    "name": "Staff & Inventory Management API",
    "_postman_id": "staff-inventory-api-v1",
    "description": "Complete API collection for the Staff & Inventory Management backend.\n\n**Setup:**\n1. Set the `base_url` variable to `http://localhost:5000`\n2. Run `POST /api/auth/login` with root/admin credentials — `token`, `user_id`, `shop_id`, and `active_shop_id` variables are auto-set\n3. All subsequent requests use the token automatically\n\n**Seed credentials:**\n- Root: root@org.com / Root@1234\n- Admin: admin@org.com / Admin@1234\n- Manager: manager@org.com / Manager@1234\n- Sub-Manager: submanager@org.com / SubMgr@1234\n- Staff: staff@org.com / Staff@1234",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:5000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "user_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "shop_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "active_shop_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "role_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "rota_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "attendance_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "location_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "item_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "query_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "🔐 Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login (Root)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.data.token);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('user_id', json.data.user.id);",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('shop_id', json.data.user.shop_id || '');",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('active_shop_id', json.data.user.active_shop_id || json.data.user.shop_id || '');",
                  "  console.log('✅ Token saved');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"root@org.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Root@1234\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Admin)",
          "event": [
            {
